gate.pass_criteria:
README.md reports ≥ 9 level-2 headers (Audience; How to Read;
Governance Domain Inventory; Audience Taxonomy Matrix; Deferred
Domains; Phantom and Forthcoming References; Pending Migrations;
Style Authority; Open Questions / Deferred Items).
Title (# ...) is level-1 and not counted; level-3 cluster headers
also not counted by this grep.
